scene.message:
Yukino: Okay. So we just{nl}
find the "Mirror Shards"{nl}
and set them in the frame.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, Mayuzumi.{nl}
The tower's guarded by{nl}
demons, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}With this crew, aren't{nl}
we a bit shorthanded?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: If you don't like{nl}
it, wait here.{waitkey}{clearbox}We don't know what dangers{nl}
lie ahead - no need to{nl}
force yourself to come.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Me, no matter what{nl}
happens, I want to save{nl}
Ms. Saeko.{waitkey}{clearbox}A delinquent screwup even{nl}
my parents gave up on -{nl}
she alone tried to save me.{waitkey}Always.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now it's my turn to save{nl}
her. My way - the way{nl}
I'm good at!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Mayuzumi...{nl}
I doubt it, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}you wouldn't think of{nl}
leaving Ayase all alone{nl}
in a place like this{wait_fr:30}, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase's coming too!!{nl}
I feel safer with Mayuzumi{nl}
and {ctl0f:1} around{color:3}♥{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Heh... Fine,{nl}
suit yourself.{waitkey}{clearbox}When things get rough,{nl}
having you around{nl}
lightens the mood.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Hey, Yuka!!{nl}
Why do you have{nl}
a gun?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Nanjo gave it to me{nl}
to hold.{waitkey}Inaba and Nanjo went to{nl}
the police for weapons.{waitkey}{clearbox}Nanjo got hurt there and{nl}
came back to school,{waitkey}{clearbox}and said "hold these while{nl}
I get treated," and handed{nl}
me a few.{waitkey}{clearbox}I snagged one in the{nl}
confusion. Ehehe{color:3}♥{color:0}{waitkey}I wanted to fire one once.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Whoa, the wind's{nl}
picking up~ So cold~{nl}
my ears hurt~{waitkey}Let's get inside quick~!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Yeah.{waitkey}Standing here won't{nl}
get us anywhere.{waitkey}{clearbox}Even to gather the{nl}
"Mirror Shards," three of{nl}
us against demons is iffy...{waitkey}{clearbox}Like Yuka says, we'd best{nl}
round up a few more{nl}
people first.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Then it's settled!{nl}
Let's get inside quick!{nl}
We'll freeze to death!{waitkey}{ret}
